Assigment 1
Lorenz Attractor

Adil Sadik (BBA student)
sadik.adil@gmail.com

Key bindings
    Arrow keys  Change view angle
    ESC         Exit
    0           Reset view angle and lorenz parameters
    s           Increase parameter s by 1
    S           Decrese parameter s by 1
    b           Increase parameter b by 1
    B           Decrese parameter b by 1
    r           Increase parameter r by 1
    R           Decrese parameter R by 1
    x           Rotate around X axis
    y           Rotate around Y axis
    z           Rotate around Z axis
    a           Enable animation
    A           Disable animation
    d           Display x,y,z axis- useful in debug 
    D           Don't display x,y,z axis- useful in debug 


Reference used:
* Code from exercise 6.
* http://www.prinmath.com/csci5229/misc/lorenz.c 


Time took to complete the assignment: ~5 hours

